    <p>Hydroxycut is the most recognized weight loss supplement brand in America, and their gummy formula centers on C. canephora robusta — a green coffee bean extract studied in two clinical trials. In the primary study, participants lost an average of 10.95 lbs over 60 days with a low-calorie diet and moderate exercise, compared to 5.40 lbs in the placebo group. The chlorogenic acid in the extract is believed to modulate glucose absorption and hepatic fat metabolism.</p>

    <div class="warn-box">
      <span class="warn-box-ico">&#9888;</span>
      <p><strong>Study transparency note:</strong> Both clinical studies cited by Hydroxycut were funded by the brand's parent company (Iovate Health Sciences). While they were published in peer-reviewed journals, independent replication is limited. The results should be interpreted as promising but not definitive. We recommend combining Hydroxycut with a structured diet and exercise program for realistic expectations.</p>
